---
title: Portobello Burrito Bowl with Pico de Gallo and DIY Pickled Jalapeños
description: The juicy portobello mushroom takes it's well-earned spot on center stage with fresh cilantro rice as its co-star. Pico de Gallo and DIY pickled jalapenos make standout extras in this soon-to-be award-winning dish!
